# Governance and constitutional code — Governance panel required
/crates/exo-governance/ @exochain/governance
/crates/decision-forum/ @exochain/governance
/governance/ @exochain/governance

# Legal compliance — Legal panel required
/crates/exo-legal/ @exochain/legal
/crates/exo-consent/ @exochain/legal
/TERMS-CONDITIONS-AND-PRIVACY.md @exochain/legal

# Demo platform — Operations panel
/demo/ @exochain/operations
/demo/infra/ @exochain/operations

# CI/CD and deployment — Operations panel
/.github/workflows/ @exochain/operations
/Dockerfile @exochain/operations
/docker-compose.yml @exochain/operations

# Documentation — all panels for their respective areas
/docs/ @exochain/architecture
/docs/council/ @exochain/governance

# Constitutional documents — require Governance + Legal
/EXOCHAIN_Specification_v2.2.pdf @exochain/governance @exochain/legal
/CONTRIBUTING.md @exochain/governance
